    <p>AM­S­TER­DAM • Ajax Am­s­ter­dam de­fender Da­ley Blind says he is “feel­ing fine” af­ter he col­lapsed dur­ing Tues­day’s pre-sea­son foot­ball friendly against Hertha Berlin when his im­planted de­fib­ril­la­tor mo­men­tar­ily switched off.</p>
    <p>He dropped to the ground late in the game but was then able to walk off the pitch. Blind was di­ag­nosed with heart mus­cle in­flam­ma­tion af­ter ex­pe­ri­enc­ing dizzi­ness in a Cham­pi­ons League game last year.</p>
    <p>He re­turned to ac­tion in Fe­bru­ary.</p>


